description.en:
TheDogeWorld is a community based token with an upcoming decentralized exchange (DEX) for NFT marketplace, which would enable our members to design and auction Doge related NFT.

It aims to build an ecosystem, centered around the Doge community, by providing value based offerings and benefits to its members.

TheDogeWorld’s 3 dimensional reward plan of money(Dogecoin), virtue (charity) and growth(community support) highlights it’s passion and commitment to the Doge community.

7% of all transactions are redistributed to holders as Dogecoin, the ever so popular open-source digital currency with current market cap rank of 7 and an all-time high market cap of $80 bn, drawing attraction from the likes of Elon Musk!
